def appendMS(circ, ids):
    circ.insert(len(circ), {'R': {ids[0]}})
    circ.insert(len(circ), {'MSd': {ids}})
    circ.insert(len(circ), {'Q': {ids[0]}})
    circ.insert(len(circ), {'Q': {ids[1]}})
    circ.insert(len(circ), {'Rd': {ids[0]}})

appendMS(eft, (0,4))
appendMS(eft, (1,2))

{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
k1 = 0b0001111
k2 = 0b1010101
k3 = 0b0110011
k12 = k1 ^ k2
k23 = k2 ^ k3
k13 = k1 ^ k3
k123 = k12 ^ k3
stabilizerGenerators = [k1, k2, k3]
stabilizerSet = [0, k1, k2, k3, k12, k23, k13, k123]

def hamming2(x, y):
    count, z = 0, x ^ y
    while z:
        count += 1
        z &= z - 1
    return count


def logErr(out):
    
    if min([hamming2(out, i) for i in stabilizerSet]) > 1:
        return True
    else:
        return False


functions = {"logErr": logErr}
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
init = Protocol()
init._check_fns.update(functions)
init.add_nodes_from(['ENC', 'meas'], circuits=[eft, meas])

init.add_edge('START', 'ENC', check='True')

init.add_edge('ENC', 'ENC', check='ENC[-1]==1')
init.add_edge('ENC', 'meas', check='ENC[-1]==0')

init.add_edge('meas', 'EXIT', check='logErr(meas[-1])')
draw_protocol(init)
